img2mp4 (1.0.1) stable; urgency=medium

  * One video per directory, one video for all file args; refactor to
    mkvideo_from_dir and mkvideo_from_files (Python and Bash)
  * Strip dir names from output path (Webcam, auto-shoot, camera, B612,
    DCIM, IMAGES, case-insensitive), e.g. foo/DCIM/file.jpg -> foo/file.mp4
  * With -k, remove empty parent dirs when processing directories only

 -- Lenik (谢继雷) <lenik@bodz.net>  Wed, 25 Feb 2025 00:00:00 +0000

img2mp4 (1.0.0) stable; urgency=medium

  * Initial release
  * Convert image series to video with timecode subtitles
  * Support for EXIF datetime extraction
  * Multiple subtitle themes
  * H.264/H.265 codec support

 -- Lenik (谢继雷) <lenik@bodz.net>  Mon, 01 Jan 2024 12:00:00 +0000

